name: IV. “XENOMORPH”
description:
4/8 from “Nightmares” collection.
It’s a collection created to celebrate Halloween that revives the most common and darkest nightmares that haunt the human being. 8 collectible card amulets that explain the most terrifying fears and give protection to those who have them.

Description of the piece:
The meaning of dreaming about aliens and extraterrestrials is related to a moment of great curiosity for changes that a person is experiencing or uncertainty in life or even, it can be a symptom of lack of focus on self-knowledge, since no one may have discovered a part of his personality that could surprise everyone and even him/herself. He/she could have hidden capabilities.
It’s very likely that the sleeper is having problems adjusting to his/her new reality, perhaps he/she made new friends and left some, moved to another house or has a new job, hence he/she feels distressed.
